Bangladesh Inflation Slows for Second Month in June, Agency Says

-- B y   A r u n   D e v n a t h
-- 
2011-07-13T13:34:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/bangladesh-inflation-slows-for-second-month-in-june-agency-says.html
Bangladesh inflation slowed for a
second month in June, the Bangladesh Bureau of Statistics said.  Consumer prices rose 10.17 percent last month from 10.2
percent in May, the statistics agency said in an statement in
Dhaka today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Arun Devnath in Mumbai at 
